Class StringKit

  • java.lang.Object
    • squidpony.StringKit

  • public class StringKit
extends Object
    Various utility functions for dealing with Strings, CharSequences, and char[]s; mostly converting numbers. Created by Tommy Ettinger on 3/21/2016.
